{"parentUuid":"c0a2c483-9d34-4e1c-9f7e-6e4abb0e3afe","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01JvmtoCZwtsKUQRsJ3n1tSJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_read_input_tokens":27873,"output_tokens":1671,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":1671,"cache_read_input_tokens":27873,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaDYKT8JbDSrTnedPpF7n","type":"assistant","uuid":"c8174b55-beda-4d0d-b48a-4477c19012ba","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:41:11.150Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"c8174b55-beda-4d0d-b48a-4477c19012ba","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01JvmtoCZwtsKUQRsJ3n1tSJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's the draft plan. Review before I write it.\n\n---\n\n**Project**: `whatAmIDoing` — a Claude Code plugin that educates users about their project's internals.\n\n**Deliverable**: A distributable Claude Code plugin directory with:\n- `.claude-plugin/plugin.json` manifest\n- `commands/under-the-hood.md` slash command\n- `assets/template.html` — self-contained HTML template (inline CSS/JS, Mermaid from CDN)\n- `scripts/launch.sh` — writes output HTML and opens in browser\n- `README.md` — install + usage\n\n**Flow when user runs `/under-the-hood`**:\n1. Claude detects stack by scanning manifest files (package.json, pyproject.toml, Cargo.toml, pubspec.yaml, go.mod, etc.)\n2. Claude reads top-level code samples, configs, entry points\n3. Claude produces a structured JSON analysis with these sections:\n   - Overview (1-paragraph plain-English summary)\n   - Tech Stack (each dep with: what it is, why used, layman analogy)\n   - Architecture (components, data flow — rendered as Mermaid)\n   - Key Algorithms / Logic (with complexity notes)\n   - Methodologies (testing, state mgmt, auth, etc.)\n   - Pattern Rationale (\"why this choice + tradeoffs\")\n   - Pitfalls (common mistakes for this stack)\n   - Glossary (jargon → plain English)\n4. Script injects JSON into HTML template, writes `./under-the-hood.html`, opens in default browser.\n\n**HTML features**:\n- Top toggle: **Technical ↔ Layman** view (two text variants per section)\n- Collapsible sections, sticky TOC\n- Mermaid diagrams for architecture\n- Glossary tooltips on hover\n- Optional quiz section (\"check your understanding\")\n- Dark/light theme toggle\n\n**Non-goals for v1**: git history analysis, runtime tracing, dependency graph crawling, multi-project support.\n\n**Acceptance**: installing the plugin locally, running `/under-the-hood` in a real project, produces an HTML page that correctly identifies the stack and renders all sections in both modes.\n\n---\n\nApprove this and I'll write `.framework/plan.md` and kick off the Trellis pipeline. Any changes?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_read_input_tokens":27873,"output_tokens":1671,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":1671,"cache_read_input_tokens":27873,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaDYKT8JbDSrTnedPpF7n","type":"assistant","uuid":"1145f85f-7046-4470-951e-044b9a4b7097","timestamp":"2026-04-19T17:41:20.756Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/avinkrism4pro/Personal/apps/MyApps/whatAmIDoing","sessionId":"72a03414-ba52-4106-b27a-7f28ae50fe45","version":"2.1.114","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
