{"parentUuid":"1e8c694d-d88d-4534-a804-06eb0adc7814","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"832f3565-b939-4c66-ad82-036060e8e108","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012H7Rr7VokPJus4bb9aFj8k","type":"tool_result","content":"# Plan Structure Template\n\nUse this structure when producing `plan.md`. Each section is required.\nFenced YAML blocks are machine-extracted in later phases.\n\n---\n\n## App Overview\n\n[1-3 paragraphs: what the app does, who it's for, target platform]\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n```yaml\nlanguage:\nframework:\nstate_management:\ndatabase:\ntesting:\nbuild_tool:\n```\n\n## Screens\n\n[For each screen:]\n\n### Screen: {ScreenName}\n\n- **Purpose**: [one sentence]\n- **Key interactions**: [bulleted list]\n- **Data displayed**: [what data this screen reads]\n- **Data modified**: [what data this screen writes]\n\n## Component Inventory\n\n### Layer 1: Data Components\n\n```yaml\ncomponents:\n  - name: {ComponentName}\n    responsibility: \"{one sentence}\"\n    owns: [list of files/artifacts this component produces]\n    key_complexity: \"{the hardest part}\"\n    dependencies: []\n```\n\n### Layer 2: UI Atom Components\n\n```yaml\ncomponents:\n  - name: {ComponentName}\n    responsibility: \"{one sentence}\"\n    owns: [list of files/artifacts]\n    key_complexity: \"{the hardest part}\"\n    dependencies: []\n```\n\n### Layer 3: Logic Components\n\n```yaml\ncomponents:\n  - name: {ComponentName}\n    responsibility: \"{one sentence}\"\n    owns: [list of files/artifacts]\n    key_complexity: \"{the hardest part}\"\n    dependencies: [list of Layer 1 component names this depends on]\n```\n\n### Layer 4: Theme\n\n```yaml\ncomponents:\n  - name: {ComponentName}\n    responsibility: \"{one sentence}\"\n    owns: [list of files/artifacts]\n    dependencies: []\n```\n\n## Assembly Overview","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"23157692-5ba1-4ab8-bcd4-17b91177e2a3","timestamp":"2026-04-19T23:41:16.640Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"# Plan Stru